<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>플랩사무소</title>

    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #111;
            color: white;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        .container {
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .card {
            width: 700px;
            padding: 50px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1f1f1f, #2c2c2c);
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 60px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #00ff88;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 25px;
            color: #ccc;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 20px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #e0e0e0;
        }

        .button {
            margin-top: 40px;
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 35px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            background-color: #00ff88;
            color: black;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .button:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            background-color: #00cc6a;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">

            <h1>플랩사무소</h1>

            <h2>축구를 사랑하는 사람들의 공간</h2>

            <p>
                실력 상관 없음.<br>
                열정만 있으면 누구든 환영.<br><br>

                우리는 단순한 풋살팀이 아니라<br>
                함께 뛰고, 웃고, 성장하는 팀입니다.
            </p>

            <a href="#" class="button">지금 참여하기</a>

        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
